<geoCoordinate id="62DEC4A4FFA1FFEBA6A9F822FDEEDBE8" box="[441,552,1997,2025]" degrees="04" direction="north" minutes="54" orientation="latitude" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" precision="925" value="4.9">04°54′ N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="62DEC4A4FFA1FFEBA524F822FD6FDBE8" box="[564,681,1997,2025]" degrees="58" direction="west" minutes="15" orientation="longitude" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" precision="925" value="-58.25">58°15′ W</geoCoordinate>
]; 
<specimenCode id="574C0A18FFA1FFEBA5ACF820FC95DBE9" box="[700,851,1998,2025]" collectionCode="MZUF" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/mvk4-k796" name="Museo Zoologico La Specola, Universita di Firenze" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">MZUF 1798</specimenCode>
.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="4FF0F1E8FFA0FFEAA7ADFEE7FD6BDD9B" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0755A263FFA0FFEAA7ADFEE7FE90DD23" blockId="57.[189,342,264,290]" box="[189,342,264,290]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
<heading id="5C1D150FFFA0FFEAA7ADFEE7FE90DD23" bold="true" box="[189,342,264,290]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" reason="3">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA7ADFEE7FE90DD23" bold="true" box="[189,342,264,290]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Distribution</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0755A263FFA0FFEAA7ADFED7FD6BDD9B" blockId="57.[188,1400,312,411]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
The type locality, Marlissa, is probably the name of a river in the 
<collectingRegion id="C52E6C81FFA0FFEAA4C6FED7FA93DD53" box="[982,1365,312,338]" country="Guyana" name="Upper Demerara-Berbice" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Upper Demerara-Berbice region</collectingRegion>
of 
<collectingCountry id="7FFDE2F3FFA0FFEAA7AFFEB3FED8DD77" box="[191,286,348,374]" name="Guyana" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Guyana</collectingCountry>
. The precise locality could not be located, hence the coordinates provided are an approximation of where the 
<typeStatus id="D8511CC1FFA0FFEAA646FE6EFE4FDD9A" box="[342,393,385,411]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">type</typeStatus>
specimen was collected.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="4FF0F1E8FFA0FFEAA7ADFE2DFDC8DF91" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="0755A263FFA0FFEAA7ADFE2DFEE9DDDD" blockId="57.[189,303,450,476]" box="[189,303,450,476]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
<heading id="5C1D150FFFA0FFEAA7ADFE2DFEE9DDDD" bold="true" box="[189,303,450,476]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" reason="3">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA7ADFE2DFEE9DDDD" bold="true" box="[189,303,450,476]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0755A263FFA0FFEAA7ADFE1DFED8DF08" blockId="57.[188,1399,498,777]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA7ADFE1DFE5BDE0D" author="Caporiacco L. di" box="[189,413,498,524]" firstAuthor="Caporiacco" journalOrPublisher="Monitore Zoologico Italiano" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="20 - 34" part="56" refId="ref147262" refString="Caporiacco L. di. 1947. Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti. Monitore Zoologico Italiano 56: 20 - 34." title="Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti" type="journal article" year="1947">Caporiacco (1947)</bibRefCitation>
introduced the generic name 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA41AFE1DFB1DDE0D" authority="Caporiacco, 1947" authorityName="Caporiacco" authorityYear="1947" box="[778,1243,498,524]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Oligacanthophrynus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA41AFE1DFC38DE0D" box="[778,1022,498,524]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Oligacanthophrynus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA318FE1DFB1DDE0D" author="Caporiacco L. di" box="[1032,1243,498,524]" firstAuthor="Caporiacco" journalOrPublisher="Monitore Zoologico Italiano" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="20 - 34" part="56" refId="ref147262" refString="Caporiacco L. di. 1947. Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti. Monitore Zoologico Italiano 56: 20 - 34." title="Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti" type="journal article" year="1947">Caporiacco, 1947</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
with a short description of the genus. The 
<typeStatus id="D8511CC1FFA0FFEAA52BFDF9FD65DE31" box="[571,675,534,560]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA5C6FDF9FAFDDE31" authority="Caporiacco, 1947" authorityName="Caporiacco" authorityYear="1947" box="[726,1339,534,560]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Oligacanthophrynus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guianensis">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA5C6FDF9FB91DE31" box="[726,1111,534,560]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Oligacanthophrynus guianensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA374FDF9FAFDDE31" author="Caporiacco L. di" box="[1124,1339,534,560]" firstAuthor="Caporiacco" journalOrPublisher="Monitore Zoologico Italiano" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="20 - 34" part="56" refId="ref147262" refString="Caporiacco L. di. 1947. Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti. Monitore Zoologico Italiano 56: 20 - 34." title="Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti" type="journal article" year="1947">Caporiacco, 1947</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was described in more detail by 
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA508FDD5FD3FDE55" author="Caporiacco L. di" box="[536,761,570,596]" firstAuthor="Caporiacco" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="607 - 747" part="118" refId="ref147295" refString="Caporiacco L. di. 1948. Arachnida of British Guiana collected in 1931 &amp; 1936 by Professors Beccari and Romiti. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London 118: 607 - 747. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1948. tb 00402. x" title="Arachnida of British Guiana collected in 1931 &amp; 1936 by Professors Beccari and Romiti" type="journal article" year="1948">Caporiacco (1948)</bibRefCitation>
and revisited fifty years later by 
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA386FDD5FAB4DE55" author="Weygoldt P." box="[1174,1394,570,596]" firstAuthor="Weygoldt" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin of the British Arachnological Society" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="72" part="11" refId="ref155847" refString="Weygoldt P. 1998 a. The identity of Oligacanthophrynus guianensis di Caporiacco, 1947 (Arachnida: Amblypygi: Charinidae). Bulletin of the British Arachnological Society 11: 72." title="The identity of Oligacanthophrynus guianensis di Caporiacco, 1947 (Arachnida: Amblypygi: Charinidae)" type="journal article" year="1998" yearSuffix="a">Weygoldt (1998a)</bibRefCitation>
, who considered 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA692FDB1FDB0DE79" authorityName="Caporiacco" authorityYear="1947" box="[386,630,606,632]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Oligacanthophrynus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA692FDB1FDB0DE79" box="[386,630,606,632]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Oligacanthophrynus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA46AFDB1FC2EDE79" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1892" box="[890,1000,606,632]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Charinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA46AFDB1FC2EDE79" box="[890,1000,606,632]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Charinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and concluded that the specimen used in 
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA609FD6DFDCCDE9D" author="Caporiacco L. di" box="[281,522,642,668]" firstAuthor="Caporiacco's" journalOrPublisher="Monitore Zoologico Italiano" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="20 - 34" part="56" refId="ref147262" refString="Caporiacco L. di. 1947. Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti. Monitore Zoologico Italiano 56: 20 - 34." title="Diagnosi preliminari di specie nuove di aracnidi della Guiana Britannica raccolte dai Professori Beccari e Romiti" type="journal article" year="1947">Caporiacco’s (1947)</bibRefCitation>
description was a protonymph, probably conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA3A9FD6DFAFDDE9D" authorityName="Goodnight &amp; Goodnight" authorityYear="1946" box="[1209,1339,642,668]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Charinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gertschi">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA3A9FD6DFAFDDE9D" box="[1209,1339,642,668]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">C. gertschi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The characters present in the protonymph, however, are insufficient to assign 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA339FD49FB0DDEC1" authorityName="Caporiacco" authorityYear="1947" box="[1065,1227,678,704]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Oligacanthophrynus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guianensis">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA339FD49FB0DDEC1" box="[1065,1227,678,704]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">C. guianensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to any known species due to its incomplete development, so 
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFA0FFEAA417FD25FC27DEE5" author="Weygoldt P." box="[775,993,714,740]" editor="Adis J." firstAuthor="Weygoldt" journalOrPublisher="Pensoft Publishers, Moscow" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="293 - 302" refId="ref156099" refString="Weygoldt P. 2002 a. Amblypygi. In: Adis J. (ed.) Amazonian Arachnida and Myriapoda: 293 - 302. Pensoft Publishers, Moscow." title="Amblypygi" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Amazonian Arachnida and Myriapoda" year="2002" yearSuffix="a">Weygoldt (2002a)</bibRefCitation>
considered the species a nomen dubium.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0755A263FFA0FFEAA7ADFCDFFDC8DF91" blockId="57.[187,1399,815,912]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
Due to the uncertainty regarding the systematics of the species in the Guianas and 
<collectingCountry id="7FFDE2F3FFA0FFEAA37CFCC0FB14DF48" box="[1132,1234,815,841]" name="Suriname" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Surinam</collectingCountry>
, it is presently impossible to determine the identity of 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFA0FFEAA58DFCBCFCF9DF6D" authorityName="Caporiacco" authorityYear="1947" box="[669,831,851,877]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Oligacanthophrynus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guianensis">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFA0FFEAA58DFCBCFCF9DF6D" box="[669,831,851,877]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">C. guianensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and shall remain so until adult specimens are collected at the 
<typeStatus id="D8511CC1FFA0FFEAA666FC99FE6FDF91" box="[374,425,886,912]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
